result_quotes: Patient: Sort of, like I just, I found it really hard to get out of bed this morning.
Medical Student: OK, I, I think, I don't think I asked this, but have you had any surgeries before?
Patient: I had cataract surgery done.
Medical Student: And uhm, have you had any, uhm, problems with swallowing, like food or liquids?
Patient: No, I don't think so. I just had breakfast this morning and no problems there.
Medical Student: Have you had any diarrhea or constipation?
Patient: Uhm, I'm often constipated but nothing new there.
